content_vision: Finds a new love that has not been expected
text:
Verse 1:
Didn't see it coming, but you hit me like a ton of bricks,
now I can't imagine life without your loving and your tricks.
Never believed in love at first sight,
but with you, it just felt so right.
Lost in your mesmerizing gaze,
I knew I had found my soulmate,
You showed me that destiny is real,
and in your arms, I finally feel

Chorus 1:
I never knew I needed this love, but now I can't imagine living without it,
you're my everything and I'll never doubt it.
With you, I've found a love that makes everything else fade,
and I never want to let it slip away.

Verse 2:
Every time our lips meet,
it's like a perfect symphony,
Every moment with you feels like a dream come true,
I never thought I'd find someone like you.
Underneath all the superficiality, we found a love that was real and pure,
proving that sometimes what we need most is something we never could've predicted or seen before.
Fate brought us together, despite the odds,
our love was meant to be, like we were written in the stars above.

Chorus 2:
Our love defies the rules and breaks all the norms,
but in each other's arms, we've weathered every storm.
Our love is like a fairytale, a dream come true,
never thought I'd find someone like you.

Chorus 3:
Falling for you opened my eyes,
I never knew love could feel so right.
Falling for you opened my eyes, I never knew love could be this sweet,
and with you, I found the missing piece that made me complete.

Bridge:
Lost in the chaos of life, I never thought I'd find someone who made everything feel right. But here we are,
in each other's arms, our love blazing brighter than a shooting star.
Lost in your love, I've found myself,
all my fears and doubts, vanished into thin air.

Outro:
As we ride off into the sunset, I know our love was something we never could've regret
And as our story continues, together we'll overcome any challenge we may meet Because with you by my side, my love, there's nothing we can't beat.

Theme melody:
Couldn't have imagined it, a love like this,
we fit together like a perfect melody.

Instrumental:
In this moment, with just the sound of our hearts beating in sync,
everything else fades away, our love is all that we'll ever need.

struct_suggs.name: Emotional Build-Up Ballad
attrs: has a short and punchy introduction
includes a prechorus that builds up to the chorus
has a strong bridge that adds a different musical element to the song
includes a distinct outro that wraps up the song
features an instrumental section with a prominent melodic theme
allows for a guitar or instrumental solo
has a clear ending with an "end bridge"

struct_suggs.name: Energetic Chorus Melody
attrs: has a strong and catchy chorus as the main focal point
includes two verses with distinct melodies
allows for a bridge to break up the repetition of verses and choruses
has a clear outro that ends the song
features an instrumental section, possibly with a solo or melodic theme
has a well-defined structure that can be easily followed by listeners

struct_suggs.name: Dynamic Intro Flow
attrs: starts off with a strong intro to capture the listener's attention
includes a verse and chorus, followed by a prechorus that builds up to the next chorus
has a bridge to add variety to the song
has a distinct outro that wraps up the song
features an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure
can create a gradual build-up towards the end of the song

struct_suggs.name: Bridge and Solo Blend
attrs: has a catchy chorus as the main focal point
features two distinct verses with different melodies
includes a bridge to add variety and break up the repetition of verses and choruses
has a clear outro that wraps up the song
includes an instrumental section that can showcase a melodic theme or solo
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure, making it suitable for a longer song

struct_suggs.name: Progressive Prechorus Build
attrs: has a short and attention-grabbing introduction
includes a prechorus that builds up to the chorus
features two distinct choruses to add variety
has a bridge that can showcase a different musical element
allows for a guitar or instrumental solo
includes a prominent melodic theme in the instrumental section
has a clear and distinct ending that wraps up the song

struct_suggs.name: Elevated Verse Flow
attrs: starts off with a strong intro that sets the tone for the song
includes a verse and chorus, followed by a prechorus that builds up to the next chorus
has a well-structured bridge that adds variety to the song
has a distinct outro that wraps up the song
features an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure, making it suitable for longer songs
can create a gradual build-up towards the finale

struct_suggs.name: Repetitive Chorus Impact
attrs: includes a strong intro that captures the listener's attention
has a clear verse and chorus structure
features two repetitions of the chorus, separated by a bridge
has a distinct and well-defined outro that ends the song
includes an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure, making it suitable for longer songs
can create a dynamic build-up towards the end of the song

struct_suggs.name: Soulful Bridge Melody
attrs: has a strong and catchy chorus as the main focal point
includes a verse with a distinct melody
has a well-structured bridge to add variety to the song
has a clear and defined outro that wraps up the song
features an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure, making it suitable for longer songs

struct_suggs.name: Dynamic Prechorus Solo
attrs: starts off with a strong intro that immediately grabs the listener's attention
includes a verse, prechorus, and chorus to create a build-up towards the bridge
has a well-structured bridge that showcases a different musical element
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure, making it suitable for longer songs
features an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
has a clear and distinct ending that wraps up the song
can create a dynamic build-up towards the finale

struct_suggs.name: Outro Solo Climax
attrs: has a strong and attention-grabbing intro
includes a verse and chorus structure, followed by a bridge that adds variety to the song
has a distinct outro that wraps up the song
features an instrumental section with a potential solo or melodic theme
allows for multiple repetitions of the verse-chorus-bridge structure
has a clear ending with an "end bridge" that adds a final touch to the song
can create a gradual build-up towards the end of the song.
